    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Might be Java 10 has what you (and I) want, through the <code>var</code> &quot;keyword&quot; (technically an identifier, see comments).</p>\n<pre><code>var list = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();  // infers ArrayList&lt;String&gt;\nvar stream = list.stream();          // infers Stream&lt;String&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>From <a href=\"http://openjdk.java.net/jeps/286\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">JDK Enhancement Proposals 286</a></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Update:</strong> Yap, that feature made it into the Java 10 release!</p>\n"
